# Dropdown rule: never use Ant `Select` in embedded UI

Ant Design popup layers are unreliable in this app layout.
For dropdown/select UX in `demo/s3-browser/ui/src`, always use:

- `SimpleSelect` for select/dropdown choices
- `SimpleAutoComplete` for searchable free-text suggestions

Do **not** introduce or reintroduce Ant `Select` / `AutoComplete` components in this UI.

